Package Boundary

Class MovieGoerUI

java.lang.Object
Boundary.UserUI
Boundary.MovieGoerUI
Direct Known Subclasses:
GuestUI
public class MovieGoerUI extends UserUI
This Class represents the UI interface for MovieGoers. It extends the abstract UserUI class and provides the implementation for the showSelections and showUI methods. This Class contains 2 key methods: showSelections and showUI to display the list of actions available for MovieGoers and to handle inputs. The other methods below are helper functions that call the static methods of Controllers.
